{"tid":331004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］點樣幫到我男朋友？","createTime":"2017-07-21T17:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T14:31:54.000Z","uid":107205,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7923925df202d9be94b1d336904ce6724ddf0bfd","tid":331004,"uid":107205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"我家境唔錯，有做嘢加part time，所以同男朋友搬左出黎住<br />\n<br />\n但男朋友經濟環境唔好，所以租金同屋企主要開支大部分都係我出，出街食飯都係我比錢<br />\n<br />\n我其實唔介意，因為佢好錫我又無可能偷食。<br />\n<br />\n但佢有壞習慣飲酒食煙，雖然唔係好重癮但未戒。<br />\n而且佢份人懶散，打唔到長工亦無乜責任心<br />\n<br />\n咁樣落去，我自己係經濟或者其他方面都辛苦<br />\n點樣真係可以幫到佢又減輕到我負擔？"},{"pid":"9102cf5f66b6acbe050ffe9f007857a899a5c75b","tid":331004,"uid":83531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"40e06ae1c32a2726b2415f6ac95c928f17584ac2","tid":331004,"uid":53794,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:45:31.000Z","msg":"廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食煙飲酒又窮又唔想打工"},{"pid":"04dfb9563c00fce2361b40e5f369ca71cf7b8650","tid":331004,"uid":50956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:47:19.000Z","msg":"認真 分手。<br />\n短期嚟講你可能好開心活係你同佢嘅世界到<br />\n仲諗方法幫佢<br />\n但長遠嚟講好辛苦"},{"pid":"1d281ed6f58f0dd5017a99f82e23dc92e3b65864","tid":331004,"uid":20291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食煙飲酒又窮又唔想打工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔煙唔酒又勤力番工但冇女，有冇人可以幫我"},{"pid":"ffc50c7e0b546030a072d5f0c8f4e3db6d453b88","tid":331004,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:48:51.000Z","msg":"佢真係執到................."},{"pid":"dfdea6377474df41ab8def5603f69247f399f9b4","tid":331004,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:49:18.000Z","msg":"btw當初咁都搬出黎住? 邊度住? 租? 供緊?"},{"pid":"9dd42123c1b528a1953385a42f7329c51b59c892","tid":331004,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw當初咁都搬出黎住? 明知男方唔多掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <del> 邊度住? 租? 供緊</del>?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8ab39139f41ed45b208979afbb240883376d4248","tid":331004,"uid":47867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:50:04.000Z","msg":"無計<br />\n佢唔做野唔肯付出真係咩都做唔到<br />\n唯有要同佢用心傾<br />\n傾唔到就要諗下分手啦"},{"pid":"e613922036742c5f29416f970667acf6528ac436","tid":331004,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"23800000<br />\nCall我吖"},{"pid":"8d19116b7168a662c9a8d8e6373a8ef5b221ef9e","tid":331004,"uid":34069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢真係執到.................</blockquote><br />\nAGGER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ca239823931c90ee36a334aa18fa713f6d4d6c","tid":331004,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:51:55.000Z","msg":"做男人做到咁，你都真係算吧啦！<br />\n同佢講，為左你地將來，正正經經去揾野做，如果唔係，都係分手吧！"},{"pid":"77d3184726d2e329f76b4c2c23671b3c8e30961e","tid":331004,"uid":53127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"長貧難顧，你幫佢等於害左佢<br />\n遲早為錢鬧交，然後分手<br />\n幾年後你會發現晒左時間落去而後悔<br />\n但係你已經係一個比人任玩幾年既老雞<br />\n有條件既人唔會理你<br />\n而你只會周圍搵人埋單<br />\n最後可能係嫁唔出或者嫁比毒，肥，mk仔<br />\n呢個就係你最後人生<br />\n如果唔想咁，及早離開"},{"pid":"7fff94b0730ca1b50255e35ffddededd244f158d","tid":331004,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"你男朋友點解要人幫呀？佢生活得好好啊，又有煙又有酒，又唔使做嘢，有女朋友養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a817ed95b12b64f642abc489480c515521813fdb","tid":331004,"uid":107205,"like